assay_description: Inhibition of alanine racemase in Mycobacterium tuberculosis H37Rv at 5 times MIC preincubated for 16 hrs followed by compound re-addition with L-Ala-[13C]-[3H] measured over 8 hrs by LC-MS/MS analysis

Inhibition of alanine racemase in Mycobacterium tuberculosis H37Rv assessed as remaining activity at MIC preincubated for 16 hrs followed by L-Ala-[13C]-[3H] addition measured over 8 hrs by LC-MS/MS analysis
